Class NumericLiteral

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.rdf4j.model.impl.SimpleLiteral
      • org.eclipse.rdf4j.model.impl.NumericLiteral
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Literal, Value

    public class NumericLiteral
extends SimpleLiteral
    An extension of SimpleLiteral that stores a numeric value to avoid parsing.
    Author:
    David Huynh
    See Also:
